Class AbstractUISocketElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.AbstractUISocketElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUISocketElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UISocketCommand, UISocketCommandParam, UISocketNotification, UISocketSet, UISocketVariable, UISocketXmlVariable

    public abstract class AbstractUISocketElement
extends Object
implements IUISocketElement
    AbstractUISocketElement is an abstract implementation of the IUISocketElement interface. It provides for the common functionality all UI Socket Elements require.
